parts.text:
```json
{
"application": "Singularity",
"software": [
"Singularity",
"Bash",
"xz"
],
"resources": [
"SLURM",
"Data directory",
"Configuration files",
"Output directory",
"Temporary directory",
"Singularity image"
],
"configuration_files": [
"do_sim.sh",
"aao_rad.inp",
"gsim.inp",
"user_ana.tcl"
],
"output_files": [
"gsim_no_gpp.bos.xz",
"all.root"
],
"environment_variables": [
"TMPDIR",
"SINGULARITY_CACHEDIR",
"JOB_DIR",
"CONFIG_DIR",
"OUTPUT_DIR",
"DATA_DIR",
"DATE",
"TYPE"
],
"commands": [
"module load singularity/2.6.0",
"singularity shell -B $DATA_DIR:/data \
		  -B $TMPDIR:/code \
		  -B $DATA_DIR/parms/recsis:/recsis \
		  $DATA_DIR/clas6.img -c \"cd /code && bash do_sim.sh\"",
"xz -9 -v -T4 $TMPDIR/gsim_no_gpp.bos",
"cp $TMPDIR/gsim_no_gpp.bos.xz $OUTPUT_DIR/gsim/npip/gsim_no_gpp_${TYPE}_${SLURM_ARRAY_JOB_ID}_${SLURM_ARRAY_TASK_ID}.bos.xz",
"cp $TMPDIR/all.root $OUTPUT_DIR/npip/${TYPE}_${SLURM_ARRAY_JOB_ID}_${SLURM_ARRAY_TASK_ID}.root",
"du -sh $TMPDIR",
"rm -rf $TMPDIR"
],
"script_type": "Bash script",
"purpose": "Running a simulation using Singularity"
}
```
